                     <interp inst="t18450818-1736-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the 2nd of Aug., 94 cheroots, value 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18450818-name-841" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-841" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
